title: 10/08/21 DPS Hour 2 Bill Plaschke

description:
Los Angeles Times Writer and Sports Columnist Bill Plaschke joins The Dan Patrick show and previews the NLDS matchup between the Dodgers and the Giants. Bill says the Dodgers will have all the pressure on them and thinks the MLB Playoffs should have seeding.
